Implement Merge sort in Java.

Given an array of N elements sort the array in ascending order using merge sort

========================================
INPUT
========================================


 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|   5   |   13   |   75   |   2   |   25   |   6   |   10   |   8   |
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



========================================

           M E R G E
             S O R T

========================================




========================================
OUTPUT
========================================

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|   2   |   5   |   6   |   8   |   10   |   13   |   25   |   75   |
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------